OL,3,C'A suffocating situation': What is
OL,4,Clife like inside an asylum-seeker
OL,5,Chotel?
OL,7,FAs protestors gathered outside a hotel
OL,8,Fhousing asylum-seekers in Long Eaton,
OL,9,Fone refugee told ITV News Central that
OL,10,Fhe finds it "suffocating" to be told
OL,11,Fto stay inside for his safety
OL,13,FAn asylum-seeker living in a hotel in
OL,14,FDerbyshire has described the
OL,15,Fexperience as "suffocating".
OL,17,FAnti-asylum protesters have continued
OL,18,Fto demonstrate outside the Long Eaton
OL,19,Fhotel after the local council voted to
OL,20,F'consider' legal action to close it
OL,21,Fdown.
