OL,3,C'A suffocating situation': What is
OL,4,Clife like inside an asylum-seeker
OL,5,Chotel?
OL,7,FProtestors want the 160 asylum-seekers
OL,8,Fliving there to be moved to
OL,9,Falternative accommodation.
OL,11,FOne protestor told ITV News Central:
OL,12,F"It was quite surprising really
OL,13,Fbecause a lot of the different parties
OL,14,Fagreed which is uncommon. So it's a
OL,15,Fgood start, but we'll see what happens
OL,16,Fnext."
