OL,3,C'A suffocating situation': What is
OL,4,Clife like inside an asylum-seeker
OL,5,Chotel?
OL,7,FAnother said: "I think we're in danger
OL,8,Fof losing a lot of our traditional
OL,9,Fways as British people. When you're
OL,10,Fhaving other peoples' cultures forced
OL,11,Fupon you."
OL,13,FWhen asked how other cultures have
OL,14,Fbeen forced upon her, the protestor
OL,15,Fsaid: "I don't get forced to do
OL,16,Fanything, I do what I want."
OL,18,FInside the hotel, asylum-seekers are
OL,19,Ftold by security to stay in their
OL,20,Frooms. Some get support from a local
OL,21,Frefugee centre.
