OL,3,C'A suffocating situation': What is
OL,4,Clife like inside an asylum-seeker
OL,5,Chotel?
OL,7,FOne asylum-seeker who has been living
OL,8,Fat the hotel for five months and who
OL,9,Fvisits the refugee centre told ITV
OL,10,FNews Central that his future is
OL,11,Funcertain.
OL,13,FHe said: "The first time I came here,
OL,14,FI had doubt and uncertainty and fear.
OL,15,FI think it would be challenging for me
OL,16,Fto go to a new city and try to meet as
OL,17,Fmany new people as I have in Long
OL,18,FEaton."
