OL,3,C'A suffocating situation': What is
OL,4,Clife like inside an asylum-seeker
OL,5,Chotel?
OL,7,FWhen asked how he feels regularly
OL,8,Fseeing protestors outside his window,
OL,9,Fhe said: "It's really unlike British
OL,10,Fpeople. Being in that suffocating
OL,11,Fsituation without anything to do, it
OL,12,Freally messes with your head."
OL,14,FCouncillor James Dawson, Leader of
OL,15,FErewash Borough Council told ITV News
OL,16,FCentral: "As the local planning
OL,17,Fauthority, Erewash Borough Council has
OL,18,Fa legal duty to assess potential
OL,19,Fbreaches of planning rules and take
OL,20,Fenforcement action if necessary.
