OL,7,F"In line with the council's
OL,8,Fconstitution, senior council officers
OL,9,Fwill now consider whether the change
OL,10,Fof use of the Best Western on Bostocks
OL,11,FLane from a commercially operating
OL,12,Fhotel to an asylum hotel is having a
OL,13,Fsufficient impact on the local area to
OL,14,Fjustify seeking a legal injunction
OL,15,Fagainst its use.
OL,17,F"This will take account of the
OL,18,Fprecedent set by Epping Forest
OL,19,FDistrict Council, where an injunction
OL,20,Fwas initially granted, and then
OL,21,Foverturned.
